How do I update this listing?




                                             Graticule Asia Macro Advisors is based out of New York. Graticule Asia Macro Advisors is a hedge fund  with  11-25 clients and discretionary assets under management (AUM) of $8,826,342,776 (Form ADV from 2017-03-30).  Their last reported 13F filing for Q1 2017 included $1,717,494,000 in managed 13F securities
    and a top 10 holdings concentration of 45.01%. Graticule Asia Macro Advisors's largest holding is SPDR S&P 500 ETF Index Depositary Receipts with shares held of 1,292,200.   WhaleWisdom has at least 9 13F filings in our database for Graticule Asia Macro Advisors. 
                                           














